  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a retrospective study. The investigators shall review the angiography data of 1200
      consecutive cardiac catheterizations of children and babies with CHD (Congenital Heart
      Disease) since 1998 till now.

      Coronary artery origin and course will be evaluated in relation to the morphologic cardiac
      anomalies.

      Coronary artery anomalies will be described and statistical analysis will be performed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
